## ui_component_refactor_plan

### Current Progress
- **Phase 1: Align with page model** — ✅ Complete
- **Phase 2: Section metadata** — ✅ Complete
- **Phase 3: Integration primitives** — ✅ Complete
- **Phase 4: Component registry & bind-point contracts** — ✅ Complete
- **Phase 5: Open derived/custom sections to registered components** — 🟡 In progress
- **Phase 6: Convert routes to dynamic page rendering** — ⬜ Not started
- **Phase 7: Add versioning and migration** — ⬜ Not started

### Phase 4 Deliverables
- [x] Component registry in `backend/internal/s_registry/component.go` with 11 canonical component definitions (7 primitive, 4 compound)
- [x] Bind-point contracts: key, label, description, kind, required, fallback on every component
- [x] Style target lists on every component for safe style override validation
- [x] `ValidateComponentConfig()` validates: component_type known, bind-point keys exist, required bind-points mapped, style-override targets and properties safe
- [x] Content validation pipeline wired: derived_section and custom_section configs validated at save time
- [x] API endpoints: `GET /config/components` and `GET /config/components/{type}` mounted in config handler
- [x] 14 focused unit tests in `component_test.go` — all passing
- [x] Full backend test suite passing (19 s_registry tests, all packages green)
- [x] Frontend types: `BindPointKind`, `BindPoint`, `ComponentDefinition` added to `types.ts`
- [x] `FactTableConfig` extended with `component_type`, `component_version`, `bindings`, `style_overrides`
- [x] TypeScript compiles cleanly with zero errors
- [x] Plan terminology updated: `LandingSection` → `PageSection`, `LandingItem` → `PageItem`
- [x] `backend_spec` updated with component registry endpoints
- [x] Verification: `go test ./...` all pass, `tsc --noEmit` clean

### Next Steps
- [x] 2026-06-09: Added component picker UI in `DerivedSectionBlock` and `CustomSectionBlock`.
- [x] 2026-06-09: Added bind-point mapping UI (column → bind-point) for derived/custom sections with `ComponentBindMapper`.
- [x] 2026-06-09: Added component-driven row rendering for derived/custom section rows with `ComponentGrid`.
- [ ] Continue Phase 5 by adding component group rendering/editing to derived/custom sections.
- [ ] Add focused tests for component-rendered section behavior when the frontend test harness is normalized.
- [ ] Verify the newly refactored UI components as part of `.todo/live_testing`

